+ RC=1        CJC=7.306p  VJC=0.75  MJC=0.3333  FC=0.5
+ CJE=22.01p  VJE=0.75   MJE=0.3333
+ TR=46.91n   TF=411.1p  ITF=0.6  VTF=1.7  XTF=3  RB=10 )

